						<div class="postbody">I'm not sure what you mean about CHR A12. My idea is to connect CHR-RAM like you would on UNROM. Meaning the MMC1 wouldn't be controlling CHR at all. Modding an existing board might be hard. But part of the idea is if you needed more capacity a PCB with MMC1 clone could be designed with this high capacity method in mind.</div>

